headline: Why Fidelity National Financial, VICI Properties, And Skyworks Solutions Are Winners For Passive Income
summary: Companies with a long history of paying dividends and consistently hiking them remain appealing to income-focused investors. Fidelity National Financial, VICI Properties, and Skyworks Solutions have rewarded shareholders for years and recently announced dividend increases. These companies currently offer dividend yields of around 3% to 5%.
